---
title:  Sweet Corn and Bell Pepper Tacos with chipotle aioli and cheese
description: The taco is a staple of Mexican cuisine today enjoyed around the world. These veggie tacos are super quick to create with standout elements including a creamy chipotle mayo and delicious cubes of golden fried cheese.
